column9: The Capital. The Kremlin. Red Square. Bolshoi Theatre.
Cultural Capital. The Hermitage. White Nights. Venetial canals.
Capital of the Urals. Romanov final site. Border of Europe/Asia.
Capital of Siberia. Trans-Siberian railway hub. Academic Town (Akademgorodok).
'Third Capital'. Kazan Kremlin (UNESCO). Mix of Tatar and Russian cultures.
Port of Five Seas. Gateway to the Caucasus. Cossack heritage.
Pacific terminus of Trans-Siberian. Golden Horn Bay bridge.
2014 Winter Olympics. Black Sea summer resort.
